flowchart TD
    DEV([👨‍💻 Developer]) -->|git push| GH[GitHub Repository]
    GH -->|triggers| GA[GitHub Actions\nCI/CD Pipeline]
    GA -->|docker build\nkubectl apply| MK

    subgraph MK[🏗️ Minikube Cluster]
        subgraph APP[Default Namespace]
            NA[kubeheal-app\nNode.js Pod\nreplicas: 2]
            AI[ai-analyzer\nFastAPI Pod]
        end

        subgraph MON[Monitoring Namespace]
            PR[Prometheus\nmetrics store]
            GR[Grafana\ndashboards]
            PR -->|visualize| GR
        end

        NA -->|/metrics\nscrape| PR
        AI -->|reads pod logs\nvia K8s API| NA
    end

    NA -->|crash\nprocess.exit 1| CRASH[💥 Pod Crashes\nrestart_count++]
    CRASH -->|Kubernetes\ndetects via\nliveness probe| NA

    CRASH -->|restart_count ≥ 3| HL

    subgraph HL[🔧 heal.py - runs on Mac]
        H1[1. detect unhealthy pod]
        H2[2. call ai-analyzer]
        H3[3. get root cause + fix]
        H4[4. delete pod]
        H1 --> H2 --> H3 --> H4
    end

    H4 -->|kubectl delete pod| NA
    AI -->|diagnosis +\nsuggested fix| H3

    style MK fill:#1a1a2e,stroke:#4a90d9,color:#fff
    style APP fill:#16213e,stroke:#4a90d9,color:#fff
